PN,36401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784274472
OL,3,CMum killed in train crash after safety
OL,4,Cbarriers 'weren't activated'
OL,6,FTraffic lights and safety barriers at
OL,7,Fa level crossing where a mum was
OL,8,Fkilled when a train hit her car "had
OL,9,Fnot been activated", investigators
OL,10,Fhave revealed.
OL,12,FKerry Coombes was killed when the
OL,13,FNorthern passenger service struck her
OL,14,Fcar at the Hoghton automatic half-
OL,15,Fbarrier level crossing, between
OL,16,FPreston and Blackburn, on Thursday, 25
OL,17,FJune at 8.48am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784274472
OL,3,CMum killed in train crash after safety
OL,4,Cbarriers 'weren't activated'
OL,6,FHer eight-year-old daughter, who was a
OL,7,Fpassenger in the car, suffered serious
OL,8,Finjuries in the collision and remains
OL,9,Fin hospital. Nobody on board the train
OL,10,Fwas injured.
OL,12,FFollowing the incident an urgent probe
OL,13,Fwas launched by the Rail Accident
OL,14,FInvestigation Branch (RAIB), who
OL,15,Findependently investigates accidents
OL,16,Fand serious incidents on UK railways.
OL,18,FInitial findings from the watchdog
OL,19,Fhave revealed a critical failure in
OL,20,Fthe crossing's automated safety
OL,21,Fsystems.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784274472
OL,3,CMum killed in train crash after safety
OL,4,Cbarriers 'weren't activated'
OL,6,FThe barriers on the crossing on
OL,7,FStation Road had not been lowered and
OL,8,Fan alarm which is meant to alert
OL,9,Fpedestrians when a train approaches
OL,10,Fdid not sound, the findings said.
OL,12,FA preliminary investigation also found
OL,13,Fthat moments before the fatal
OL,14,Fcollision the train, the 7.51am
OL,15,FNorthern service from Colne to
OL,16,FPreston, passed through a green
OL,17,Fsignal, allowing it to proceed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784274472
OL,3,CMum killed in train crash after safety
OL,4,Cbarriers 'weren't activated'
OL,6,FA full, independent investigation is
OL,7,Fnow underway to determine the exact
OL,8,Fsequence of events that led to the
OL,9,Ffatal incident.
OL,11,FInvestigators say their probe will
OL,12,Ffocus heavily on the actions of those
OL,13,Finvolved and any factors that may have
OL,14,Finfluenced them.
OL,16,FIt will also look at the history of
OL,17,Fthe crossing, including any previous
OL,18,Fsafety incidents, as well as the
OL,19,Foverall management of risk and any
OL,20,F"underlying systemic factors that
OL,21,Fcontributed to the failure".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784274472
OL,3,CMum killed in train crash after safety
OL,4,Cbarriers 'weren't activated'
OL,6,FChris Wright, Network Rail's North
OL,7,FWest Route Director, said: "The
OL,8,Finitial findings published by the Rail
OL,9,FAccident Investigation Branch (RAIB)
OL,10,Ftoday are an important step in helping
OL,11,Fus understand what happened and why.
OL,13,F"In addition to continuing our own
OL,14,Finvestigation, we are also fully
OL,15,Fcooperating with RAIB and the Office
OL,16,Fof Rail and Road (ORR) and will
OL,17,Fcarefully consider any findings as
OL,18,Fthey emerge and act swiftly on lessons
OL,19,Flearned.
OL,26,@oD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784274472
OL,3,CMum killed in train crash after safety
OL,4,Cbarriers 'weren't activated'
OL,6,F"There have been no previous incidents
OL,7,Fof this nature at Hoghton level
OL,8,Fcrossing, and we carried out several
OL,9,Fsafety checks and reviews to ensure
OL,10,Fthat the crossing was safe to reopen."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, more than 1,000 people have
OL,13,Fput their names to a petition urging
OL,14,FNetwork Rail and Lancashire County
OL,15,FCouncil to permanently close the
OL,16,FStation Road crossing.
OL,26,@rD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
